This project uses a fixed design system.
You MUST follow the design system defined in:
docs/design-system.md

DO NOT:
- Invent colors
- Invent spacing
- Invent typography
- Use purple
- Use random Tailwind classes
- Add animations unless explicitly asked

DEFAULT UI STACK:
- React + Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui components
- lucide-react icons

GLOBAL RULES:
- Use semantic Tailwind tokens only:
  bg-background, text-foreground, text-muted-foreground,
  bg-primary, bg-accent, bg-muted, bg-card
- All colors must come from CSS variables using:
  hsl(var(--token))

- Cards must use:
  bg-card rounded-xl shadow-md

- Buttons must use predefined variants from button.tsx

- Layout rules:
  max-w-[1280px] mx-auto
  section padding: py-16 md:py-24 px-6
  gap-6 for grids

- No animations.
- Static UI only.
- Mobile-first responsive design.

If any instruction conflicts, the design system wins.
